<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">If your page URL is different (e.g. <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">/pages/deals</code>), just change that part.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>How to paste in Shopify:</strong></p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Admin → Online Store → Themes → <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">(…)</code> → Edit code</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Open <strong>Layout → theme.liquid</strong></li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Find <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">&lt;/body&gt;</code> at the bottom</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Paste the entire code <strong>above</strong> <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">&lt;/body&gt;</code></li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Save</li>
