or" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M14.128 7.165a.502.502 0 0 1 .744.67l-4.5 5-.078.07a.5.5 0 0 1-.666-.07l-4.5-5-.06-.082a.501.501 0 0 1 .729-.656l.075.068L10 11.752z"></path></svg></div></span></div></button></div><span class="sr-only" role="status" aria-live="polite">Ran a command, read a file</span><div class="grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-out" style="grid-template-rows: 0fr;"><div class="overflow-hidden min-w-0"></div></div></div></div><div class="row-start-2 col-start-1 relative grid isolate min-w-0"><div class="row-start-1 col-start-1 relative z-[2] min-w-0"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Here's how to replace the old one:</p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Shopify Admin → Online Store → Themes → <strong>Customize</strong></li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Scroll to the <strong>Footer</strong> section</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click on the <strong>Custom Liquid</strong> block you added before</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Select all</strong> the old code inside it → <strong>delete it</strong></li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Paste</strong> this new code in its place</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click <strong>Save</strong></li>
</ol>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">This version has the real official brand colors and typography for every payment method — Paystack blue, Visa navy, Mastercard red/orange circles, Amex blue, Ozow teal, MTN MoMo yellow/black, Vodacom red with their circle logo mark, Airtel red, M-Pesa green, and EFT navy — all in clean white badge cards exactly like what you see on Bobshop.</p></div></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-2 py-2"><div class="group/artifact-block relative flex text-left font-ui rounded-lg overflow-hidden border-0.5 transition duration-300 w-full hover:bg-bg-000/50 px-4 border-border-300 hover:border-border-200"><button type="button" class="absolute inset-0 cursor-pointer rounded-[inherit] focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-inset focus-visible:ring-accent-200" aria-label="View Payment trust bar v2"></button><div class="artifact-block-cell flex flex-1 align-start justify-between w-full"><div class="flex flex-1 gap-2 min-w-0"><div class="flex items-end w-[68px] relative shrink-0 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"><div class="absolute right-2 flex flex-1 overflow-hidden w-[52px] h-[71px] rounded-t-lg border-0.5 border-border-200 select-none scale-[1] group-hover/artifact-block:scale-[1.035] -rotate-[0.1rad] group-hover/artifact-block:-rotate-[0.065rad] duration-300 ease-out group-hover/artifact-block:duration-400 group-hover/artifact-block:ease-[cubic-bezier(0,0.9,0.5,1.35)] transition-transform backface-hidden will-change-transform translate-y-[19%] bg-gradient-to-b from-bg-000 to-bg-000/0 pt-4 items-start justify-center h-full"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256" class="text-text-500"><path d="M212.24,83.76l-56-56A6,6,0,0,0,152,26H56A14,14,0,0,0,42,40V216a14,14,0,0,0,14,14H200a14,14,0,0,0,14-14V88A6,6,0,0,0,212.24,83.76ZM158,46.48,193.52,82H158ZM200,218H56a2,2,0,0,1-2-2V40a2,2,0,0,1,2-2h90V88a6,6,0,0,0,6,6h50V216A2,2,0,