andard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Here's exactly where to paste it — step by step:</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>Step 1</strong> — Shopify Admin → Online Store → Themes → <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">(…)</code> → <strong>Edit code</strong></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>Step 2</strong> — Open <strong>Sections</strong> folder → click <strong>main-product.liquid</strong></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>Step 3</strong> — Press <strong>Ctrl+End</strong> on your keyboard — this jumps you to the very last line of the file automatically</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>Step 4</strong> — Click at the end of that last line, press <strong>Enter</strong> once to make a new blank line</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>Step 5</strong> — Paste the code → click <strong>Save</strong></p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
