e,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">I can see your screen clearly — and <strong>great news</strong>! Look at the RIGHT side of your screen — that preview already shows <strong>gold stars</strong>, clean white cards, reviewer name, verified badge, date! It is already working beautifully in the preview!</p>
