  select-none
  disabled:pointer-events-none
  disabled:opacity-50
  disabled:shadow-none
  disabled:drop-shadow-none border-transparent
          transition
          font-base
          duration-300
          ease-[cubic-bezier(0.165,0.85,0.45,1)] h-8 w-8 rounded-md backdrop-blur-md _fill_10ocf_9 _ghost_10ocf_96" type="button" aria-label="Copy to clipboard" data-state="closed"><div class="relative"><div class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" style="width: 20px; height: 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M12.5 3A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 14 4.5V6h1.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 17 7.5v8a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5 1.5h-8A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 6 15.5V14H4.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 3 12.5v-8A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 4.5 3zm1.5 9.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5 1.5H7v1.5a.5.5 0 0 0 .5.5h8a.5.5 0 0 0 .5-.5v-8a.5.5 0 0 0-.5-.5H14zM4.5 4a.5.5 0 0 0-.5.5v8a.5.5 0 0 0 .5.5h8a.5.5 0 0 0 .5-.5v-8a.5.5 0 0 0-.5-.5z"></path></svg></div><div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center"><div class="transition-all opacity-0 scale-50" style="width: 20px; height: 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="transition-all opacity-0 scale-50" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M15.188 5.11a.5.5 0 0 1 .752.626l-.056.084-7.5 9a.5.5 0 0 1-.738.033l-3.5-3.5-.064-.078a.501.501 0 0 1 .693-.693l.078.064 3.113 3.113 7.15-8.58z"></path></svg></div></div></div></button></div></div><div class="text-text-500 font-small p-3.5 pb-0">css</div><div class="overflow-x-auto"><pre class="code-block__code !my-0 !rounded-lg !text-sm !leading-relaxed p-3.5" style="color: rgb(20, 24, 31); background: transparent; font-family: var(--font-mono);"><code class="language-css" style="color: rgb(20, 24, 31); background: transparent; font-family: var(--font-mono); white-space: pre;"><span><span class="token token class" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24);">.jdgm-star</span><span> </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">{</span><span> </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24);">font-family</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">:</span><span> </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(0, 128, 0);">'JudgemeStar'</span><span> </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;">!important</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">;</span><span> </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24);">color</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">:</span><span> </span><span class="token token hexcode color">#F5A623</span><span> </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;">!important</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">;</span><span> </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">}</span><span>
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token class" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24);">.jdgm--on</span><span> </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">{</span><span> </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24);">color</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">:</span><span> </span><span class="token token hexcode color">#F5A623</span><span> </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;">!important</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">;</span><span> </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">}</span><span>
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token class" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24);">.jdgm--off</span><span> </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">{</span><span> </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24);">color</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">:</span><span> </span><span class="token token hexcode color">#ddd</span><span> </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;">!important</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">;</span><span> </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">}</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>Step 2</strong> — Inside Judge.me go to <strong>Widgets → Review Widget → click the green "Install" button</strong> to reinstall the widget fresh on your product page. Judge.me recommends reinstalling the Star Rating Badge and Review Widget to restore full functionality. <span class="inline-flex" data-state="closed"><a href="https://judge.me/help/en/articles/8200629-reinstalling-judge-me-widgets-when-changing-your-theme" target="_blank" class="group/tag relative h-[18px] rounded-full inline-flex items-center overflow-hidden -translate-y-px cursor-pointer"><span class="relative transition-colors h-full max-w-[180px] overflow-hidden px-1.5 inline-flex items-center font-small rounded-full border-0.5 border-border-300 bg-bg-200 group-hover/tag:bg-accent-900 group-hover/tag:border-accent-100/60"><span class="text-nowrap text-text-300 break-all truncate font-normal group-hover/tag:text-text-200">Judge.me</span></span><span class="transition-all opacity-[0%] h-[17px] absolute right-[0.5px] rounded-r-full flex items-center px-1.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-900/0 via-accent-900/100 via-30% to-accent-900/100 group-hover/tag:opacity-[100%]"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256" class="transition-all group-hover/tag:ease-out duration-[500ms] ease-in text-accent-100 group-hover/tag:scale-[100%] scale-[80%] group-hover/tag:opacity-[100%] opacity-[0%] -mr-[2px]"><path d="M200,64V168a8,8,0,0,1-16,0V83.31L69.66,197.66a8,8,0,0,1-11.32-11.32L172.69,72H88a8,8,0,0,1,0-16H192A8,8,0,0,1,200,64Z"></path></svg></span></a></span></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>Step 3</strong> — After reinstalling, go back to <strong>Judge.me → Widgets → Review Widget</strong> and send me a screenshot — I need to see if you have the <strong>new version or legacy version</strong> because the layout shown in the theme editor may not match what you configured in your Judge.me admin — you need to switch the block preview from Sample data to Real data to see the correct layout. <span class="inline-flex" data-state="closed"><a href="https://judge.me/help/en/articles/8420649-customizing-the-review-widget-legacy-version" target="_blank" class="group/tag relative h-[18px] rounded-full inline-flex items-center overflow-hidden -translate-y-px cursor-pointer"><span class="relative transition-colors h-full max-w-[180px] overflow-hidden px-1.5 inline-flex items-center font-small rounded-full border-0.5 border-border-300 bg-bg-200 group-hover/tag:bg-accent-900 group-hover/tag:border-accent-100/60"><span class="text-nowrap text-text-300 break-all truncate font-normal group-hover/tag:text-text-200">Judge.me</span></span><span class="transition-all opacity-[0%] h-[17px] absolute right-[0.5px] rounded-r-full flex items-center px-1.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-900/0 via-accent-900/100 via-30% to-accent-900/100 group-hover/tag:opacity-[100%]"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256" class="transition-all group-hover/tag:ease-out duration-[500ms] ease-in text-accent-100 group-hover/tag:scale-[100%] scale-[80%] group-hover/tag:opacity-[100%] opacity-[0%] -mr-[2px]"><path d="M200,64V168a8,8,0,0,1-16,0V83.31L69.66,197.66a8,8,0,0,1-11.32-11.32L172.69,72H88a8,8,0,0,1,0-16H192A8,8,0,0,1,200,64Z"></path></svg></span></a></span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 pointer-coarse:opacity-100 transition" role="group" 