n-300 ease-out" style="grid-template-rows: 0fr;"><div class="overflow-hidden min-w-0"></div></div></div></div><div class="row-start-2 col-start-1 relative grid isolate min-w-0"><div class="row-start-1 col-start-1 relative z-[2] min-w-0"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Here is why this will work when nothing else did — it uses 3 layers:</p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Injects immediately</strong> when page loads</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Watches the page</strong> using MutationObserver — the moment Judge.me adds any element to the page it fires again instantly</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Safety net</strong> — fires again after 1 second AND 3 seconds to catch any late loading</li>
</ol>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>Where to paste — same file as your Netflix popup:</strong></p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Edit code → <strong>Layout → theme.liquid</strong></li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Press <strong>Ctrl+F</strong> → search <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">&lt;/body&gt;</code></li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Paste <strong>above</strong> <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">&lt;/body&gt;</code></li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click <strong>Save</strong></li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">On your phone — close browser completely → reopen your product page</li>
