<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Save</li>
</ol>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>What it gives you:</strong></p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">A small green circular cart icon button (exactly like Takealot's) appears next to every product card in "You might also like", collection grids, AND on the main product page</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click it → button <strong>shakes</strong> 🔄</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Item gets <strong>added to cart automatically</strong> via Shopify's cart API — no page reload</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Button turns green with checkmark for a second ✅</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">A small dark toast pops up at the bottom saying "Added to cart!"</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Your cart icon count updates automatically</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">It works on ALL products automatically — no manual setup per product needed. It watches your page and adds the button to any product card it finds, including ones that load later (like related products).</p></div></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-2 py-2"><div class="group/artifact-block relative flex text-left font-ui rounded-lg overflow-hidden border-0.5 transition duration-300 w-full hover:bg-bg-000/50 px-4 border-border-300 hover:border-border-200"><button type="button" class="absolute inset-0 cursor-pointer rounded-[inherit] focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-inset focus-visible:ring-accent-200" aria-label="View Shake add to cart"></button><div class="artifact-block-cell flex flex-1 align-start justify-between w-full"><div class="flex flex-1 gap-2 min-w-0"><div class="flex items-end w-[68px] relative shrink-0 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"><div class="absolute right-2 flex flex-1 overflow-hidden w-[52px] h-[71px] rounded-t-lg border-0.5 border-border-200 select-none scale-[1] group-hover/artifact-block:scale-[1.035] -rotate-[0.1rad] group-hover/artifact-block:-rotate-[0.065rad] duration-300 ease-out group-hover/artifact-block:duration-400 group-hover/artifact-block:ease-[cubic-bezier(0,0.9,0.5,1.35)] transition-transform backface-hidden will-change-transform translate-y-[19%] bg-gradient-to-b from-bg-000 to-bg-000/0 pt-4 items-start justify-center h-full"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256" class="text-text-500"><path d="M212.24,83.76l-56-56A6,6,0,0,0,152,26H56A14,14,0,0,0,42,40V216a14,14,0,0,0,14,14H200a14,14,0,0,0,14-14V88A6,6,0,0,0,212.24,83.76ZM158,46.48,193.52,82H158ZM200,218H56a2,2,0,0,1-2-2V40a2,2,0,0,1,2-2h90V88a6,6,0,0,0,6,6h50V216A2,2,0,0,1,200,218Z"></path></svg></div></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-1 py-4 min-w-0 flex-1"><div class="leading-tight text-sm line-clamp-1">Sh