2><div class="font-claude-response relative leading-[1.65rem] [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:bg-bg-000/50 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-0.5 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-border-400 [&amp;_.ignore-pre-bg&gt;div]:bg-transparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Perfect. Monthly subscription via Paystack. Now let me build the full Sky Blueprint platform.</p></div></div><div class="mt-4"><div class="grid grid-rows-[auto_auto] min-w-0"><div class="row-start-1 col-start-1 min-w-0"><div class="min-w-0 pl-2 py-1.5"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><button class="group/status flex items-center gap-2 py-1 text-sm transition-colors cursor-pointer text-left text-text-500 hover:text-text-300 flex-1 min-w-0" aria-expanded="false"><div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 min-w-0" style="opacity: 1;"><span class="truncate font-base">Created 4 files, ran 2 commands, read a file</span><span class="inline-flex transition-transform duration-200 shrink-0 -rotate-90"><div style="width: 12px; height: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M14.128 7.165a.502.502 0 0 1 .744.67l-4.5 5-.078.07a.5.5 0 0 1-.666-.07l-4.5-5-.06-.082a.501.501 0 0 1 .729-.656l.075.068L10 11.752z"></path></svg></div></span></div></button></div><span class="sr-only" role="status" aria-live="polite">Created 4 files, ran 2 commands, read a file</span><div class="grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-out" style="grid-template-rows: 0fr;"><div class="overflow-hidden min-w-0"></div></div></div></div><div class="row-start-2 col-start-1 relative grid isolate min-w-0"><div class="row-start-1 col-start-1 relative z-[2] min-w-0"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>Sky Blueprint is ready!</strong> Download the ZIP above. Here is everything explained:</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>What's built:</strong></p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Beautiful dark landing page with fingerprint logo, gradient blue/purple branding</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Pricing page — Free Trial / R99 Pro / R249 Business</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Login &amp; Signup with accounts saved locally</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Full dashboard with all 6 tools</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Paystack payment integration — money goes straight to your bank</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>To go live — 3 things to do:</strong></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>1. GitHub (free hosting)</strong><br>
Follow the README inside the ZIP — takes 10 minutes</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>2. Get your Paystack keys</strong></p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Go to <strong>paystack.com</strong> → sign up → verify your SA ID</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Create subscription plans (R99/month, R249/month)</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Copy your public key and plan codes</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Paste them into <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">app.js</code> where it says <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">pk_test_xxxxxxx</code></li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>3. Receive money</strong><br>
Every time someone subscribes, Paystack collects the money and deposits it into your SA bank account automatically — daily. You see every payment on your Paystack dashboard.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>Phone tracking app</strong> — tell me when you are ready and I will build the Android APK as the next step.</p></div></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-2 py-2"><div class="group/artifact-block relative flex text-left font-ui rounded-lg overflow-hidden border-0.5 transition duration-300 w-full hover:bg-bg-000/50 px-4 border-border-300 hover:border-border-200"><button type="button" class="absolute inset-0 cursor-pointer rounded-[inherit] focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-inset focus-visible:ring-accent-200" aria-label="View Sky blueprint"></button><div class="artifact-block-cell flex flex-1 align-start justify-between w-full"><div class="flex flex-1 gap-2 min-w-0"><div class="flex items-end w-[68px] relative shrink-0 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"><div class="absolute right-2 flex flex-1 overflow-hidden w-[52px] h-[71px] rounded-t-lg border-0.5 border-border-200 select-none scale-[1] group-hover/artifact-block:scale-[1.035] -rotate-[0.1rad] group-hover/artifact-block:-rotate-[0.065rad] duration-300 ease-out group-hover/artifact-block:duration-400 group-hover/artifact-block:ease-[cubic-bezier(0,0.9,0.5,1.35)] transition-transform backface-hidden will-change-transform translate-y-[19%] bg-gradient-to-b from-bg-000 to-bg-000/0 pt-4 items-start justify-center h-full"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256" class="text-text-500"><path d="M212.24,83.76l-56-56A6,6,0,0,0,152,26H56A14,14,0,0,0,42,40V216a14,14,0,0,0,14,14H200a14,14,0,0,0,14-14V88A6,6,0,0,0,212.24,83.76ZM158,46.48,193.52,82H158ZM200,218H56a2,2,0,0,1-2-2V40a2,2,0,0,1,2-2h90V88a6,6,0,0,0,6,6h50V216A2,2,0,0,1,200,218Z"></path></svg></div></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-1 py-4 min-w-0 flex-1"><div class="leading-tight text-sm line-clamp-1">Sky blueprint</div><div class="text-xs line-clamp-1 text-text-400 opacity-100 transition-opaci