up-hover/btn:group-aria-pressed/btn:bg-accent cds-btn-squish "></span><span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 "><span class="relative"><span data-cds="Icon" class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" aria-hidden="true" style="font-family: var(--font-anthropicons, Anthropicons-Variable); font-feature-settings: &quot;liga&quot; 0; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-style: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; line-height: 1; width: 1em; height: 1em; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; user-select: none; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 433.3;"></span><span data-cds="Icon" class="absolute inset-0 transition-all opacity-0 scale-50" aria-hidden="true" style="font-family: var(--font-anthropicons, Anthropicons-Variable); font-feature-settings: &quot;liga&quot; 0; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-style: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; line-height: 1; width: 1em; height: 1em; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; user-select: none; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 433.3;"></span></span></span></button><div class="flex items-center"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="[content-visibility:auto] [contain-intrinsic-size:auto_400px] px-2 -mx-2 pb-8 -mb-8 print:[content-visibility:visible]"><div data-test-render-count="2"><div class="group" style="height: auto; opacity: 1; transform: none;"><div class="contents"><div data-is-streaming="false" class="group relative relative pb-3" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><h2 class="sr-only select-none">Claude responded: Smart thinking — focus on getting customers first, then build the app when you have money coming in.</h2><div class="font-claude-response relative leading-[1.65rem] [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:bg-bg-000/50 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-0.5 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-border-400 [&amp;_.ignore-pre-bg&gt;div]:bg-transparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Smart thinking — focus on getting customers first, then build the app when you have money coming in. That is exactly how successful businesses grow.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>So your plan right now is:</strong></p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">✅ Sky Blueprint website — <strong>built and ready</strong></li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">✅ Pricing set — R300 website + R55/month subscription</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">⏳ <strong>GitHub</strong> — go do those 4 phases now and make it live</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">⏳ <strong>Paystack</strong> — set up your account to receive money</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">⏳ <strong>Market it</strong> — get your first customers</li>
</ol>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>While you go do GitHub — here is what to do on Paystack after:</strong></p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Go to <strong>paystack.com</strong> → Sign up free</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Verify your SA ID and bank account</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Create two plans:
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Plan 1: <strong>Sky Blueprint Monthly</strong> → R55/month</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Plan 2: <strong>Sky Blueprint Website</strong> → R300 once-off</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Copy your <strong>Public Key</strong> from the dashboard</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Open <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">app.js</code> → find the line that says <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">pk_test_xxxxxxx</code> → replace it with your real key</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Re-upload <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">app.js</code> to GitHub → your payments go live</li>
</ol>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>Go do GitHub now</strong> — come back when it is live and send me your GitHub URL. I will check it is working perfectly and then guide you through Paystack setup step by step.</p>
