l-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Here are two descriptions — one for the website and one for when you market Sky Blueprint:</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>🌐 Website Description (what visitors read on the site):</strong></p>
<blockquote class="ml-2 border-l-4 border-[hsl(var(--border-300)/0.1)] pl-4 text-text-300">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Sky Blueprint is a South African digital platform that gives entrepreneurs, job seekers and professionals everything they need to succeed online — all in one place, for one low monthly price. From building your own website to cleaning your emails, tracking your phone, planning your business with AI, building your CV and finding jobs — Sky Blueprint has it all. No contracts. No hidden fees. Just powerful tools built for South Africans, by a South African.</p>
</blockquote>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>📱 Social Media / Marketing Description (for Facebook, TikTok, Instagram):</strong></p>
<blockquote class="ml-2 border-l-4 border-[hsl(var(--border-300)/0.1)] pl-4 text-text-300">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">🔵 Introducing <strong>Sky Blueprint</strong> — the all-in-one digital platform built for South Africa! 🇿🇦</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">For just <strong>R55/month</strong> you get access to 6 powerful tools:<br>
🌐 Website Builder — get your business online<br>
📧 Email Cleaner — never miss an important email<br>
📍 Find My Phone — track your device on SA map<br>
🤖 AI Business Mentor — grow your business 24/7<br>
📄 CV Builder — build your CV and find jobs on LinkedIn &amp; Indeed<br>
🗺️ SA Map — explore South Africa live</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Want us to build your professional website? Only <strong>R450 once-off.</strong><br>
Prefer to pay less long term? Get our <strong>3-Year Plan for R1,980</strong> — that's 36 months of full access!</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">👉 Sign up free today — 7-day trial, no credit card needed.<br>
🔗 skyblueprint.github.io</p>
</blockquote>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Want me to also write you a <strong>WhatsApp broadcast message</strong> to send to your contacts to get your first customers?</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 pointer-coarse:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><button type="button" data-cds="Button" class="cds-reset group/btn relative isolate inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center gap-1.5 whitespace-nowrap select-none cursor-[var(--cds-cursor-interactive)] aria-disabled:cursor-default data-[disabled]:cursor-default border-0 outline-none rounded h-control font-sans text-body font-medium [&amp;:disabled:not([aria-busy])]:opacity-50 disabled:pointer-events-none transition-shadow duration-fast focus-visible:shadow-focus text-primary aria-pressed:text-accent aspect-square w-control px-0 !text-muted hover:!text-primary" aria-label="Copy" data-testid="action-bar-copy" id="base-ui-_r_1ei_"><span aria-hidden="true" class="absolute -z-[1] rounded-[inherit] transition-colors duration-fast group-focus-visible/btn:shadow-[inset_0_0_0_1px_var(--cds-page-bg)] bg-transparent group-hover/btn:bg-fill-ghost-hover group-aria-expanded/btn:bg-fill-ghost-hover inset-0 group-aria-pressed/btn:bg-accent group-hover/btn:group-aria-pressed/btn:bg-accent cds-btn-squish "></span><span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 "><span class="relative"><span data-cds="Icon" class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" aria-hidden="true" style="font-family: var(--font-anthropicons, Anthropicons-Variable); font-feature-settings: &quot;liga&quot; 0; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-style: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; line-height: 1; width: 1em; height: 1em; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; user-select: none; font-